text: Prof. Tareq Al-Hamouri, Jordanian politician and minister. He held the position of minister of industry trade and supply in the government of Omar Razzaz from June 14, 2018 to the year 2020, he was awarded his PHD in comercial law from The University of Bristol (UK). == References == Category:Living people Category:Jordanian politicians Category:1975 births
title: Tareq Hammouri
